<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="slice-n">slice <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /slaɪs/    美 /slaɪs/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>薄片；切片：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>slice of bread</strong> / ham
一片面包/火腿</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>cut</strong> the meat <strong>into</strong> thin <strong>slices</strong>
把肉切成薄片</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>份；部分：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a big / large <strong>slice of</strong> income
收入中的一大部分</p></div></div>